"datePublished\">Jul 14, 2022\n          </time></p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div class=\"post-content e-content\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n        <p>Travel more when you are young.</p>\n\n<p>Looking back at my 20s, I don‚Äôt remember much about the 100s of projects I delivered, but I do remember:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Backpacking across Bhutan</li>\n  <li>Sleeping under the star lit sky at half moon beach in Gokarna</li>\n  <li>Almost drowning on the way to Maya beach</li>\n  <li>Rafting in Halong bay</li>\n  <li>Bus hopping from one beach to another in Sri Lanka</li>\n  <li>Getting punched by a random stranger in Thailand</li>\n  <li>Chennai monsoons, because I used to go there to meet my gf/ now wife</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>As you grow older, you spend a lot of time in nostalgia. It is hard to be nostalgic when you don‚Äôt have any memories and each day overlaps with the other.</p>\n\n<p>Also as you grow older, and senior in your career, you don‚Äôt have the luxury to travel. I now travel once a year maybe, even less. Even then I am on zoom most of the time.</p>\n\n<p>It is okay. <a href=\"https://manassaloi.com/2022/01/21/the-price.html\">It is my choice</a>.</p>\n\n<p>But I feel glad that I spent a lot of my 20s travelling, writing about it, and also took a lot of photos.</p>\n\n<p>In your pursuit for the next level in the job ladder, don‚Äôt forget to create memories.</p>\n\n      </div><a class=\"u-url\" href=\"/2022/07/14/travel-more.html\" hidden></a>\n    </article>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n    </main><footer class=\"site-footer h-card\">\n  <data class=\"u-url\" href=\"/\"></data>\n\n  <div class=\"wrapper\">\n\n    <div class=\"footer-col-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"footer-col one-half\">\n      <p class=\"footer-heading\"> Powered by <a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com\">Jekyll</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/minima\">Minima.</a> ¬© Manas J Saloi.</p>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer-col one-half\" style=\"text-align: right;\">